## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of studies reviewed. The findings are primarily based on studies conducted during or shortly after the COVID-19 pandemic, which may not fully represent the long-term impacts of online learning. Additionally, the report does not account for variations in online learning quality or differences in student demographics, which can significantly influence outcomes.

